 \"from\": 712, \"to\": 719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a surprise for Casey and executive producer Ben Winston, who initially wanted to make the performance as easy as possible for Tom to take part.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Winston\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Winston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surprise\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"Casey\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"executive producer\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The original idea was a person in the stadium as a stunt double,\\\" Casey recalled.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The original idea\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunt\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"Casey\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are like, 'Well, there is no way we are getting this.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to get four hours of filming time.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four hours\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"filming time\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will do the thing in LA with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe we will get the other stuff and the rest will be just a stunt double.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other stuff\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tom wanted to really be a part of the performance.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Ben could not help but gush over his commitment to the project.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"his commitment\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think there is anybody like him in the world,\\\" he told The Hollywood Reporter last month.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0787698424631495e-37, \"text\": \"The Hollywood Reporter\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hollywood_Reporter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no better collaborator.\\\"\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no better collaborator\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, when the producer informed the Mission: Impossible actor that a stunt double would do the heavy lifting, he replied, \\\"We are not doing a stuntman in a balaclava.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the producer\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mission\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"Impossible actor\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunt\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the heavy lifting\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"a stuntman\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"a balaclava\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to be the one who jumps off the roof, and I am going to be the one who drives through Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967014901, \"rank\": 3.298443077539819e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for why they wanted Tom for the honor?\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the honor\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not really think who else would work,\\\" Ben admitted to the outlet.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who else is synonymous with action and an American hero?\\\"\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.998312886121056, \"rank\": 0.0016524829151689227, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 62-year-old's stunt that closed the chapter on this year's Olympic Games will surely go down in history.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 62-year-old's stunt\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the chapter\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Tom dove into the stadium, LA Mayor Karen Bass and Simone Biles presented him with the Olympic flag before he took it back to Los Angeles in true Mission: Impossible fashion.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}, {\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2210, \"en